<TITLE> 53 arrested from Postogola </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, July 10 (bdnews24.com)RAB arrested 53 people on charges of indecent conduct from two launches anchored at Postogola in the capital on Friday. Sub-inspector of South Keraniganj Police Station Kabir Ahmed said a team of RAB-10 arrested 42 women and 11 men from Ovijatri and MV Sun at Postogola crematorium area. Kabir said some local people were had been arranging recreational tour for Tk 500 every Friday. 
